<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Page Not Found - 404</title>
    <style>
        body { background: #0f172a; color: white; font-family: sans-serif; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; height: 100vh; margin: 0; }
        h1 { color: #6366f1; font-size: 5rem; margin: 0; }
        p { font-size: 1.2rem; }
        a { color: #6366f1; text-decoration: none; border: 1px solid #6366f1; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 8px; transition: 0.3s; }
        a:hover { background: #6366f1; color: white; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>404</h1>
    <p>Oops! This page doesn't exist.</p>
    <a href="index.html">Go Back Home</a>
</body>
</html>
